(1582, 160230, '2012-09-27 15:15:12', '"Neuropeptide Y-expressing cells were found in all\nlayers of the CA3 region, with the majority found within the\nstratum oriens and stratum radiatum (Fig. 6A, Table 2)."', 'p 558 left', 'data', NULL, NULL),
