(1595, 160240, '2012-09-27 15:15:12', '"As previously reported, there were\nfew calbindin-expressing cells outside the granule cell\nlayer of the dentate gyrus (Freund and Buzsaki, 1996). Of\nthese cells, most were found in the molecular layer, with\nthe remainder being found in the hilus (Table 2)."', 'p 558 right', 'data', NULL, NULL),
