(1788, 160542, '2012-09-27 15:15:15', '"The neuropeptide Y2 receptor is strongly expressed by Schaffer collateral/\ncommissural fibers in the CA1 stratum radiatum and oriens\n(Stanic et al., 2006), and Ivy cells, with their dense axons in these\nlayers, represent a major potential local source of NPY."', 'p 925 left bot', 'data', NULL, NULL),
