(1931, 160760, '2012-09-27 15:15:17', '"The other markers were\nexpressed only in a few NG [CA1 neurogliaform] cells or non-NG interneurons in a\ncomparable proportion. For example, b-NOS [nitric oxide synthase] was detected in 7 of\n15 NG cells and in 7 of 11 non-NG cells."', 'p 6778 right ', 'data', NULL, NULL),
