(1937, 160764, '2012-09-27 15:15:17', '"Immunocytochemical experiments were also performed\nusing perfusion-fixed brain tissue. Both molecules were\ndetectable in the SLM [CA1 stratum lacunosum-moleculare], with 81% of NPY[neuropeptide Y]-positive neurons double\nlabeled for alpha-actinin-2 (Fig. 2C,D) (n =  32)."', 'p 6778 right bot', 'data', NULL, NULL),
