(2310, 150130, '2012-09-27 15:15:23', '"For one of the recorded CCK-expressing interneurons (T99d), only a very partial axon could be visualized because of weak filling. The radial dendritic pattern and the VIP expression of this cell (Acsady et al., 1996) suggested that it was a basket cell, but, because of the lack of efferent synaptic target information, we refer to it as unclassified."', 'p 9786, left mid', 'data', NULL, NULL),
