(2316, 150134, '2012-09-27 15:15:23', '"Figure 5.  Postsynaptic targets and cannabinoid receptor decoration of axonal boutons from CCK [cholecystokinin]-expressing cells.  A, Axonal boutons of an apical dendrite innervating cell (T159a) labeled by neurobiotin (green) are immunopositive for CCK, CB1 receptor, and VGLUT3 as shown by immunofluorescence (false color images).  Scalebar, 10 microm."', 'p 9788, Figure 5', 'data', NULL, NULL),
